    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.85rem;">© 2024 OldEnglish Translator. Free for personal and commercial use.</p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;">
        <a href="/privacy-policy/" style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.85rem;">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms-and-conditions/" style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.85rem;">Terms</a>
